CRS Sirrine Inc. said its CRSS Capital Inc. unit agreed in principle to buy Sithe Energies U.S.A. Inc. 's 51% interest in three independent power projects.
Terms weren't disclosed. 

Currently, CRSS Capital owns 49% of the three power projects, which are located in Pennsylvania and Michigan.
All three facilities are in the final stages of construction and start-up. 

